āryanāmasaṃgītiṭīkāyāṃ nāmamantrārthāvalokinyāṃ ṣaṭkulāvalokanādhikāras tṛtīyaḥ || gāthe dve ||

<commentary>imāṃ dvādaśatathāgatabhūmyupalakṣitāṃ gāthāṃ girāṃ pater bhāṣate smeti saṃbandhaḥ || kiṃbhūtāṃ ṣaṇmantrarājānasaṃyuktām iti vakṣyamāṇaṣaṇmantropetām || kimātmikām advayodayām iti | dvayaṃ grāhyaṃ grāhakaṃ ca | tan na vidyate yasya tad advayaṃ | udety asmād ity udayaḥ | advayasyodayo 'dvayodayaḥ | sa vidyate yasyā gāthāyāṃ sādvayodayā tāṃ bhāṣate sma || punar api kiṃviśiṣṭām | anutpādadharmiṇīṃ iti dharmadhātusvabhāvāṃ śūnyatāsvabhāvām ity arthaḥ ||</commentary>

śrīvajramaṇḍālaṃkāratantre dvādaśatathāgatabhūmayaḥ paṭhyante || samantaprabhā mahābhūmiḥ sūryamaṇḍalavac ca sā |
